@startuml deployment
!theme plain
title Deployment topology — single-node ISOLAN

node "ISOLAN host\n(Linux systemd OR Windows NSSM)" {
  artifact "message-service\n(Poetry-installed)" as Svc
  database "SQLite\n(WAL)" as DB
  folder "Rendered reports\n(filesystem)" as FS
  folder "Config\n(TOML)" as Cfg
  folder "Templates\n(manifest + Jinja2)" as Tpl
}

cloud "ETL pipelines\n(gRPC clients)" as Pipelines
node "SMTP relay" as SMTP
node "Subscribers\n(email)" as Subs
actor "Operators\n(dashboard HTTPS)" as Ops

Pipelines --> Svc : gRPC :50051 (plaintext v1)
Ops --> Svc : HTTP :8080 (dashboard)
Svc --> DB
Svc --> FS
Svc --> Cfg
Svc --> Tpl
Svc --> SMTP : aiosmtplib
SMTP --> Subs

@enduml
